<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00360/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>超过███斤异常大米，令观察到它的人把手插入大米并感觉到十分快慰。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>██市███超市<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>放置在SITE-CN-81员工休息室中<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong>我小时候把手插进米缸时总会挨骂，没想到在基金会我能每天都插——Dr.阙</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00360" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00360" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00360-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zeta-9-beta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6441401); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6441401&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610183094" alt="zeta-9-beta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6441401)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zeta-9-beta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6441401); return false;">zeta-9-beta</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1597540862 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">16 Aug 2020 01:21</span></p>
