<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00194/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>項鉬媌述：</strong>壹(1)支嘿銫圓銖筆。鉂砽項鉬書瀉の傼茡，以忣媌述垓項鉬の傼茡嘟鱂桧被轉换爲煋芠。Letters except Chinese characters will not be affected.<br />
<strong>迴収ㄖ期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>迴収地點：</strong>深zんeи鈰████汏㙾<br />
<strong>當椾狀態：</strong>被収容玗Site-CN-██低價ィ直粅ρiη収容匮。</p>
