</div>
<div id="u-credit-00194-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/coldmist" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6439634); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6439634&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610183095" alt="Coldmist" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6439634)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/coldmist" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6439634); return false;">Coldmist</a></span></p>
